WEBVTT

00:05:56.960 --> 00:06:02.400
Today, with the way things are, 
we are so involved with technology

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:05.200
that the screen is everything to us.

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:08.600
At any given point, it’s WhatsApp 
or the computer,

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:14.880
yet the truth is that life’s experiences 
don’t come through machines --

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:16.560
that you get through people.

00:06:21.280 --> 00:06:24.400
When I say people, who are those people?

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:27.400
They are the older generation 
who has the experience.

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:29.000
This is why it’s so important.

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:31.640
The last thing that I want to say